Given - I am logged in
And I am on the Page 8 of Cranial MRI
Then 'Brainstem without evidence of pathological signal changes' radio button is enabled 
And 'No details' radio button is enabled 
And 'Finding' radio button is enabled 

When I select 'Brainstem without evidence of pathological signal changes' radio button 
Then 'In the high-resolution sequences inconspicuous intra- and extrameatal cranial nerves' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'In the high-resolution sequences inconspicuous intra- and extrameatal cranial nerves' checkbox
Then checkbox is checked 

When I select 'No details' radio button
Then radio button is selected
